- `game/index.html` — Added `📊 Empire` tab button as first tab (auto-activated by `tabs.js`'s `firstTab.click()` logic); added `#panel-summary` div in content area.
- `game/styles/main.css` — Toast CSS: `#toast-container` fixed bottom-right z-900; `@keyframes toast-in/toast-out` (translateX slide); `.toast` + 8 type variant classes (border-left colour coding); mobile shrinks to full width. Summary CSS: `.summary-grid` auto-fill 230px; `.summary-card` + `__title`/`__body`; `.sum-res-row`, `.sum-stat-row`, `.sum-dipl-row` flex rows; `.sum-dipl-badge--neutral/allied/war`; `.sum-progress` + fill variants (quest=gold, ach=gold, victory=green); `.summary-empire-header/name/meta/badge`; mobile collapses to single column at ≤480px.
